Summary:	%{_pearname} - parsing of DTD files and DTD validation of XML files
Summary(pl.UTF-8):	%{_pearname} - analizowanie plików DTD oraz sprawdzanie DTD plików XML
Name:		php-pear-%{_pearname}
Version:	0.4.2
Release:	4
Epoch:		0
License:	PHP 3.0
